Package cambio.simulator.parsing

Class ScenarioDescription

java.lang.Object
cambio.simulator.parsing.ScenarioDescription
public class ScenarioDescription
extends Object
Represents an scenario description input. Can be parsed to an set, containing the experiment events such as ChaosMonkeyEvents or Generators.
Author:
Lion Wagner
